        </h1>

      </div>
      <div class="span7">
        <iframe src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/57992755?portrait=0&amp;byline=0"></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="how_it_works" class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>How it Works</h1>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="span5">
        <ol class="carousel-indicators">
          <li data-target="#how_it_works_carousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active">
            <h2><span class="number-circle">1</span>Click the TowTruck Button</h2>
            <p>When on a TowTruck-enabled site, collaboration is only a click away.</p>
          </li>
          <li data-target="#how_it_works_carousel" data-slide-to="1">
            <h2><span class="number-circle">2</span>Share the TowTruck Link</h2>
            <p>When on a TowTruck-enabled site, collaboration is only a click away.</p>
          </li>
          <li data-target="#how_it_works_carousel" data-slide-to="2">
            <h2><span class="number-circle">3</span>Wait for your Friend to Join</h2>
            <p>
              You'll see a notification when your friend joins your session.
              Now you can make use of all the wonderful features of TowTruck
            </p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>
      <div class="span7">
        <div id="how_it_works_carousel" class="carousel slide">
          <!-- Carousel items -->
          <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="a active item">
              <img src="/images/sections/how_it_works/carousel-a.png" alt="Click the TowTruck Button" />
            </div>
            <div class="b item">
              <img src="/images/sections/how_it_works/carousel-b.png" alt="Click the TowTruck Button" />
            </div>
            <div class="c item">
              <div id="towtruck_demo_cursor" style="color: rgb(190, 24, 14); top: 146px; left: 188px;">
                <img class="towtruck-cursor-img" src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Demo Cursor that moves around.">
                <span class="towtruck-cursor-name" style="background-color: rgb(190, 24, 14); color: rgb(238, 238, 238);">Comrade</span>
              </div>
              <img src="/images/sections/how_it_works/carousel-c.png" alt="Click the TowTruck Button" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Carousel nav -->
          <a class="carousel-control left" href="#how_it_works_carousel" data-slide="prev">&lsaquo;</a>
          <a class="carousel-control right" href="#how_it_works_carousel" data-slide="next">&rsaquo;</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

