<div id="features" class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Helpful Tools and Features</h1>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="how_to_install" class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>How to Install TowTruck</h1>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="span6">
        <img src="/images/sections/how_to_install/site-install-01.png" alt="The JavaScript Include" />
        <h2>Add the JavaScript Include</h2>
        <p>Simply copy and paste the TowTruck Javascript snippet below into your &lt;head&gt;&lt;/head&gt; tag on your site.</p>
        <form>
          <fieldset>
            <input type="text" class="span6 copy-input" value="<script src=&quot;https://towtruck.mozillalabs.com/towtruck.js&quot;></script>">
          </fieldset>
        </form>
      </div>
      <div class="span6">
        <img src="/images/sections/how_to_install/site-install-02.png" alt="The Button" />
        <h2>Add the Button</h2>
        <p>After you've included the TowTruck Javascript snippet, copy and paste this button anywhere onto your site. Congrats, your site is now TowTruck-enabled!</p>
        <form>
          <fieldset>
            <input type="text" class="span6 copy-input" value="<a id=&quot;towtruck-bookmarklet&quot; href=&quot;#&quot;>Call TowTruck</a>">
          </fieldset>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
